SIGNATURE=$(echo -n "$BODY" | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac "your-shared-secret" -hex | cut -d' ' -f2)
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/webhook \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "X-Signature: $SIGNATURE" \
  -d "$BODY"
```

The service uses `crypto.timingSafeEqual()` to prevent timing attacks when comparing signatures.

